{"lemma":"جَمّ","slug":"جَمّ","root":"ج.م.م","root_slug":"ج-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَمّ","root":"جمم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6213","n6219"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"many, much, numerous","examples":[{"text":"فَوَائِدُ جَمَّةٌ","english":"significant benefits; substantial benefits; great usefulness"},{"text":"وَتُحِبُّونَ الْمَالَ حُبًّا جَمًّا","english":"And you love wealth with abounding love."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/d͡ʒamm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6213","headword_ar":"جَمَّ","root":"jm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) said of water, (S,) &c., (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjm","text_ar":"استجم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; said of a thing: (TA:) and, said of water, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) the former of which is of the higher authority, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumuwmN","text_ar":"جُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after it had been drawn from;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjm~","text_ar":"استجمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~uwA","text_ar":"جَمُّوا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They became many."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~ati Albiy^oru","text_ar":"جَمَّتِ البِيْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumuwmN","text_ar":"جُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water of the well returned by degrees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and became much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant, and collected;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjm~t","text_ar":"استجمّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (S.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~ato mavaAbapN jaholihi","text_ar":"جَمَّتْ مَثَابَةٌ جَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a tropical phrase, explained in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vwb","text_ar":"ثوب"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~a","text_ar":"جَمَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkayolu","text_ar":"الكَيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAmN","text_ar":"جُمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The measure became full"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL. [But only the inf. n. is there mentioned: so that the verb may be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~a","text_ar":"جُمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see below.]) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~a Alfarasu","text_ar":"جَمَّ الفَرَسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAmN","text_ar":"جَمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjm~","text_ar":"استجمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The horse abstained from covering,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that his seminal fluid"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAw^uhu","text_ar":"مَاوُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-  Also, (aor. of the former verb as above, TA, and inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAmN","text_ar":"جَمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fatigue of the horse went away;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he recovered his strength after fatigue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he recovered from his fatigue, being left unridden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajam~a","text_ar":"اَجَمَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of which see also the pass. form, below]. (M, K.) ―         -b7-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~a","text_ar":"جَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAmN","text_ar":"جَمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. infrà,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rested;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a man [as well as of a horse]; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjm~","text_ar":"استجمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 324.) ―         -b8-  Also, said of a bone, (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It had much flesh; its flesh became much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b9-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaA","text_ar":"عَلَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, became high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: perhaps said of water in a well]. (T, TA.) ―         -b10-  Also, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumuwmN","text_ar":"جُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rose"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotafaEa","text_ar":"اِرْتَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b11-  Also, (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumuwmN","text_ar":"جُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) said of an event, (K,) of the arrival of a person, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It drew near;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it came to pass:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajm~","text_ar":"اجمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (S, Msb, K,) said of an event, of separation from another, (S, TA,) and of an object of want: (TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHm~","text_ar":"احمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [q. v.,] with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H","text_ar":"ح"},{"kind":"text","text":", in this sense, was not known to As. (TA.) ―         -b12-  And, said of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~iyaAn","text_ar":"صِلِّيَان"},{"kind":"text","text":", [two plants, inf. n. not mentioned,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It attained to the state of having a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~ap","text_ar":"جُمَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tuft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flower-bud"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~a Alkabo$i","text_ar":"جَمَّ الكَبْشِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamimati Al$~aApu","text_ar":"جَمِمَتِ الشَّاةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [perhaps a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~at","text_ar":"جَمَّت"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamamN","text_ar":"جَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ram,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was hornless."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~ahu","text_ar":"جَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to rule,] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He left it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely, water [in a well],)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to collect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajm~hu","text_ar":"اجمّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~ati Albiy^oru","text_ar":"جُمَّتِ البِيْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The well was left for its water to collect"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albiy^ora","text_ar":"البِيْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjm~","text_ar":"استجمّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He left the well for some days until its water should collect:"},{"kind":"text","text":"whence the metaphorical phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbapu safahihi","text_ar":"مَثَابَةُ سَفَهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna yasotajim~u","text_ar":"كَانَ يَسْتَجِمُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [explained in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vwb","text_ar":"ثوب"},{"kind":"text","text":",] occurring in a trad. (Har p. 68.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely, a measure, S, such as is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mak~uwk","text_ar":"مَكُّوك"},{"kind":"text","text":", K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it had what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAmN","text_ar":"جُمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajm~hu","text_ar":"اجمّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~mhu","text_ar":"جمّمهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~a","text_ar":"جُمَّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was filled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6219","headword_ar":"جَمٌّ","root":"jm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", an inf. n. used as an epithet, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiymN","text_ar":"جَمِيمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to the copies of the K, but correctly ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamama","text_ar":"جَمَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the L. (TA.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlN jam~N","text_ar":"مَالٌ جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamama","text_ar":"جَمَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Muck property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many cattle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And it is said in the Kur [lxxxix. 21],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa yuHib~uwna AlmaAla Hub~FA jam~FA","text_ar":"وَ يُحِبُّونَ المَالَ حُبًّا جَمًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they love property with much love."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, TA.) Aboo-Khirásh El-Hudhalee says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_ino tagofiri A@l~`lhuma tagofiro jam~aA"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) i. c. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If thou forgive, O God, Thou forgivest"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much"},{"kind":"text","text":"sin. (Mgh.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~` AlbuEaAqi","text_ar":"جَمّٰ البُعَاقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a trad. respecting prayer for rain, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Copious, abundant, extensive rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bEq","text_ar":"بعق"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greater,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main, portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zahiyrap","text_ar":"ظَهِيرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. midday, or mid-day in summer, &c.]: and of water; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~apN","text_ar":"جَمَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (as in some copies of the K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~apN","text_ar":"جُمَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (so in other copies of the K, and accord. to the TA: [the former app. the right: if it were the latter, the author of the K, accord. to a rule which he has seldom neglected, would have added"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlD~am~i","text_ar":"بِالضَّمِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as SM has here done, unless his transcriber have thus written by mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlfatoHi","text_ar":"بِالفَتْحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water, of a well, that has collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after it has been drawn from"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~apN","text_ar":"جَمَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place in which the water collects:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and also, this last, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water itself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA: [i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supply of water that has collected after drawing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 4, last sentence but one; and see 10, last sentence:]) the pl. (of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~apN","text_ar":"جَمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"S [or of this and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also]) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAmN","text_ar":"جِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumuwmN","text_ar":"جُمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biy^orN jam~apN","text_ar":"بِيْرٌ جَمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamuwmN","text_ar":"جَمُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAw^uwA jam~FA gafiyrFA","text_ar":"جَاوُوا جَمًّا غَفِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljam~a Algafiyra","text_ar":"الجَمَّ الغَفِيرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajam~u","text_ar":"اَجَمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gfr","text_ar":"غفر"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~N","text_ar":"جَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"People of the lowest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"basest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meanest sort."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.)       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"measuring to the head of the measure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. an inf. n., of which the verb is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~a","text_ar":"جَمَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; see 1, last sentence but two; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAmN","text_ar":"جَمَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAmN","text_ar":"جُمَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAmN","text_ar":"جِمَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","S","K"]}]}}